@startuml 歌单创建时序图

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "歌单控制器" as ListController
participant "歌单服务" as ListService
participant "数据库" as Database

User -> Frontend: 填写歌单信息\n{title, style, introduction}
Frontend -> ListController: POST /songlist/create\n{歌单数据}
ListController -> ListController: 参数验证
ListController -> ListService: createSongList(songListDTO)
ListService -> ListService: 设置创建者ID
ListService -> Database: 插入歌单记录
Database --> ListService: 返回生成ID
ListService --> ListController: 返回创建结果
ListController --> Frontend: 返回成功响应\n{歌单ID}
Frontend --> User: 显示创建成功\n跳转到歌单页

@enduml